## 4. Product Architecture

CycleWise is a two-part product:

```
Part 1 — PMOS Screening Tool (Typeform)
    School visits → QR code → form → risk score → PDF report → app download

Part 2 — CycleWise Web Application
    Daily tracking + Saathi companion + community + doctor prep tools
```

### Platform Strategy

**Phase 1 (Launch): Web application**  
Deployed on Vercel. Free to access from any phone browser. No installation required. School QR codes open directly in browser. This allows real user acquisition before investing in native app development.

**Phase 2 (Post 500 users): Flutter mobile app**  
Converted from web to Flutter for Android. Existing web users migrate to app. Play Store submission only after real user base is established.

**Language:** English only at launch. Hindi and regional languages added via i18n in Phase 2.

