## 6. User Identity System

**Requirements:**
- Display name (chosen by user — does not need to be real name)
- Email and password authentication via Firebase Auth
- Unique user ID generated automatically (invisible to user)
- Profile stores: display name, age, diagnosis status (diagnosed / undiagnosed / unsure), notification preferences
- Pseudonymous by default — community participation uses display name, not real name
- Health data stored privately — never shared, never sold

