## 13. Out of Scope (Version 1)

The following features are deliberately excluded from Version 1 to maintain focus and quality:

- Live doctor consultations (requires medical licensing)
- Calorie or weight tracking (risk of harm for users with eating disorders)
- AI diagnosis of any kind (legally prohibited)
- Hindi language support (added in Phase 2 via i18n)
- Direct messaging between users (added in Phase 2)
- iOS App Store launch (Android first)

